<div id="pf2e5b" class="pf w4f h235" data-page-no="2e5b"><div class="pc pc2e5b w4f h235"><div class="t m265 x11 he y296a ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">deviation from right brings us into bond-</div><div class="t mce x11 he y2a70 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">age and condemnation. . . . </div><div class="t m5ec x18 he y2a35 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Those who are not fully converted to </div><div class="t m5e6 x11 he y2136 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the truth frequently let their minds run </div><div class="t mf10 x11 he y297e ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">freely upon worldly business, and, although </div><div class="t m3c0 x11 he y2373 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">they may rest from physical toil upon the </div><div class="t m1f0 x11 he y21bc ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath, their tongues speak out what is in </div><div class="t m68c x11 he y1b57 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">their minds; hence these words concerning </div><div class="t mbe7 x11 he y224e ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cattle, crops, losses, and gains. All this is </div><div class="t m3bc x11 he y1ff3 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath breaking. If the mind is running </div><div class="t m558 x11 he y144a ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">upon worldly matters, the tongue will re-</div><div class="t m5f7 x11 he y2185 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">veal it; for out of the abundance of the </div><div class="t m141 x11 he y219b ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">heart the mouth </div><div class="t m1178 x38 h21 y219b ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">speaketh.&quot;—Testimonies, </div><div class="t ma2d x11 h21 y15cc ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">vol. </div><div class="t m76e x74 he y166f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2, pp. 702, 703. </div><div class="t m1bd x4a he y2187 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m9b0 x29 he y1e44 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Despite their sinful deeds, for </div><div class="t m148b x11 he y1765 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">what did the people apparently hope? </div><div class="t m3c7 x11 he y1eca ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Amos 5:18-20. </div><